OL,16,Gflat surface (with the audience taking
OL,17,Gpart in a fun trick), and learn the
OL,18,Gmaths and science behind an exciting
OL,19,Gsmoke rings demonstration. This
OL,20,Gexciting talk is suitable for anyone
